rubric.en:
Se consideră varianta ca problemă de decizie (M* = M).

Expected code/algorithm:
nondetSSDDec(A, s, M) {
  foreach (a in A) x[a] = choice(2);
  mStar = 0;
  foreach (a in A) mStar = mStar + x[a];
  if (mStar == M) return succes;
  else return failure;
}

